name: Healthy Cravings Logo Tee
description:
The whole apple represents us eating healthy foods, as well as our WHOLENESS in Christ, and the fact that we are not consuming all the deception in this world that the enemy is trying to sell us as women (Like Eve in the Garden). We're not biting THAT apple!

The Healthy Cravings Network is dedicated to develop in you cravings for healthy foods and lifestyles as well as cravings for Jesus Christ and all that He has to offer.

NOTE: This is a FITTED Women's Tee, NOT a regular T-Shirt.*
